data.description: Shopping starts just 1.5 miles away, 2.5 miles to Spanish Springs Square and 4 miles to Lake Sumter Landing Square. From your new home you can golf your way through The Villages. This well-maintained house in the center of The Villages has a roof that is five years old and an AC that is five years old and has been serviced regularly. It has two bedrooms and two bathrooms with a brand-new shower in the master suite. There is a water softener system, and the three skylights, one in the kitchen and one in each bathroom, provide great natural light. The sliding glass door is damaged, but the seller will offer a concession. Come check this property out today!
